{
  "stem": "1415.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 57,
      "text": "But I was in the attic and-- with another boy, who was the brother of another friend of my brother's who was also a policeman.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 58,
      "text": "And I stayed up there in the attic for a while.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 59,
      "text": "I don't know how long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 60,
      "text": "And we used to be taken down every once in a while.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 61,
      "text": "But while I was up there, I had that problem of wetting.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "And my brother used to beg me every night, please don't wet.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "It's coming through the ceiling, and they're going to notice, and the-- the Germans are going to-- going to start looking around.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "And-- and-- and he used to make fun of me, and they used to call me a [POLISH], I-- which means a faucet, because that-- I must have really made marks on that ceiling.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "[LAUGHS] And they-- somehow we survived that, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "And I guess they used to bring us up food, because I really don't remember that part at all.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "I remember the other-- the other-- the other child was with me was a boy, also from, naturally, from my hometown, who-- who also went through the war, too.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And when he got me down to the ghetto later on, and when I stopped being up in the attic, another selection came about.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "That was the second selection or the third or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "And he had to find me a new place, because he knew that the ghetto is going to be concentrated again or made smaller again or whatever it was.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So he hid me and my-- my little brother together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I don't remember where it was or what it was, but we were both hidden.",
      "word_count": 16
    }
  ],
